Package xyz.rk0cc.willpub.pubspec

Class PubspecManager

java.lang.Object
xyz.rk0cc.willpub.pubspec.PubspecManager
public class PubspecManager extends Object
Manager of single pubspec.yaml with giving project Path.
Each PubspecManager representing a single Path of the Dart project with can not mix uses.
Since:
1.0.0
